node.text:
Out and Back.
.
.
New illustration for @hudsonvalleybrewery in collaboration with @asisnyc and @forrest.rr .
.
Out and Back (5%) Lager brewed with German malt, orange zest and electrolytes; hopped with Hallertau Blanc.
.
Head to @hudsonvalleybrewery for more info.
.
.

node.text:
Born a morning sun, rising undefended.
.
.
Pages from my comic “Morning”, available in my store at the link in my bio.
.
.
I will be closing the shop for a  bit starting Monday so anything ordered after this weekend will be shipped out the following week!
.
.
.
